name: Super Engineering
overview:
Established in the year 1993. We, Super Engineering Works, are a reputed name among Construction Companies, Civil Contractors, Builders and Individuals for providing quality Construction Machinery and Material such as Concrete Mixer, Tower Hoist, Slab Trolley & Construction Equipments.Under the qualitative guidance of our proprietor, ‘Mr. Inderjit Jass’, we have been able to build our stand-alone place in the market.We are looking queries from in Mumbai, Maharastra.

Our Infrastructure: We have a ultra-modern infrastructure setup which is managed by our highly qualified team of professionals who are highly knowledgeable and skilled as per their respective domains. All our products are regularly lubricated and upgraded so as to ensure the hassle-free functioning and timely completion of all the tasks retaining the excellent production rate.

Our Team: As an efficient team is the backbone of an organization, we are proud to have a qualified and knowledgeable team of professionals. The continuous dedication and commitment of our employees is the core reason of our success and growth in such a shorter span of time. These professionals are employed after rigorous process of interview.

Client Satisfaction: As satisfaction of the clients is the ultimate goal of any organization, we are highly engaged in satisfying our clients by providing them the qualitative range of products. The products offered by us are made as per the set international standards and industrial guidelines.

Our Products: Concrete Mixer Concrete Mixer Mixer Machine Without Hopper Half Bag Concrete Mixer Electric Motor Concrete Mixer
